name: Puzzle Rush (mmibzz, ephemeris, joni.helen)
description:
Hop into Puzzle Rush with 9 unique puzzles! You have 1 minute to assemble as many puzzles as you can.

The game disassembles the puzzles and after that you have to assemble them back together!

Use mouse to drag puzzle pieces to correct places as quickly as possible.

Audio was not created by this team. 
Credits:
nezuai, jobro and InspectorJ
